message.body: Happy hump day! Looks like there's a sub tonight so I think I'm going to go to the 5:45 class instead...any interest?
Ugh that's frustrating! I won't be able to make the 545p class. Are you around next week? Want to do next Wed if Stacy is there?
Aww okay yeah I know, looks like she's on vacation this week. I'm going to be out of town all next week, but the week after I'm definitely game!
Sounds perfect! Also my roommate is definitely moving
Does your friend/co-worker still need a place?
She does, I let her know about your apt but she said she's looking for something cheaper so I don't think it'll work out :-(
